{"tid":929454,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動漫哲學 魯魯修定朱雀啱？","createTime":"2018-12-05T14:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T21:59:09.000Z","uid":30309,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1a28e7bcadd6e8c1981e0d1e71fc92b4e3326a","tid":929454,"uid":30309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"一個要革命改變世界<br />\n一個要由內改變<br />\n<br />\n結局魯魯修成功<br />\n<br />\n融入番落香港<br />\n攞警察做例子<br />\n大家都知依家好多不知所謂<br />\n屌唔緊要<br />\n但大家叫人唔好做<br />\n姐係唔係第二選項<br />\n又唔搞<br />\n<br />\n咁結局會點？<br />\n<br />\n利申唔係差人，唔想做"},{"pid":"416533228f72412755b30d7a5bc023d1f050fe22","tid":929454,"uid":93986,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"魯魯修，沒有破壞那有革新"},{"pid":"3147f01cf1305dfadbcb3bc8ea411a0a5d72ad19","tid":929454,"uid":150609,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"都係睇佢有冇料<br />\n<br />\n夠勁既都可以由內改變到"},{"pid":"45f1cfb58aa405e01163508690bf0f5acdd6d81f","tid":929454,"uid":34760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"修奈傑爾啱"},{"pid":"75c3b64d4af9ac50d44acf966fdc12f7fd404391","tid":929454,"uid":25601,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"要成功先要有geass"},{"pid":"f09d2740e5444d4b9de867fc355d2b1563859e8a","tid":929454,"uid":79077,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d586f1b3965d51233c733259cdbe6d4bd06bc02","tid":929454,"uid":17286,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"我毀滅了世界 又創造了世界"},{"pid":"7e1e3fffac83d7448f4dfe28820f73eb909cef06","tid":929454,"uid":6883,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"講咩都好 咪又係一班毒拎圍爐9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba974213ce52c9eae0a3ba7d2c8e7e7ae532d8f","tid":929454,"uid":110973,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"魯魯修 因為最後係佢改變左世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b5705a4b15a9eeb830f77eea0c4d219528987e","tid":929454,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"由內改變既叫改革"},{"pid":"02626f4f3d057a1341e2d2e7924c8d6fee832d6e","tid":929454,"uid":200328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"諗住由內變革<br />\n又有幾多個係可以不受環境改變而保持自我<br />\n改革一個人總比改革成個群體容易"},{"pid":"8bc08d0d7aff74cac19786ea47575ee2505922b0","tid":929454,"uid":96032,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"魯魯修嘅情況，佢哋兩個嘅目標都係獲得權力去改變當前環境<br />\n只係一個選擇慢慢打工升做高層，一個選擇直接篡位<br />\n法律上當然係前者正確<br />\n但問題係，打工升職升到一個話到事嘅位置，要用幾多時間？得到嘅權力又有幾大？足唔足夠？<br />\n畀朱雀做到軍方話事人又點，佢做嘅改變得唔到同僚同人民（大部分係不列顛人）嘅認可，最後成鬼到事咩<br />\n就算所有人都buy你，最後都有個不列顛皇帝係你頭頂，你想幫日本人爭取人權，皇帝唔肯，你仲做到啲咩？<br />\n單論魯魯修入面嘅情況，朱雀根本晒9氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港嘅情況又係點？大家心照啦"},{"pid":"6493efb42ad5667233f47b5f771baccbd5a34ed7","tid":929454,"uid":46389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"贏就革命，輸就造反<br />\n結論就係睇結果"},{"pid":"42a7055e97fedaee6d5da058345de2fb65ebfbc2","tid":929454,"uid":146340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f09d2740e5444d4b9de867fc355d2b1563859e8a","tid":929454,"uid":79077,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"原來你平時咁核突係有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b924fd9c07e3c8a003fb84923711f3bb84a8ab5","tid":929454,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a7055e97fedaee6d5da058345de2fb65ebfbc2","tid":92